{"data":[{"name":"87:1","price":"Sucikanlah nama Tuhanmu Yang Mahatinggi,","arabic":"سَبِّحِ ٱسۡمَ رَبِّكَ ٱلۡأَعۡلَى","category":["87 (Al-A'la)","Al-A'la","Surah Al-A'la"],"ayahNumber":5949,"juzNumber":30,"footnotes":"","lang":"id"},{"name":"87:2","price":"yang menciptakan, lalu menyempurnakan (penciptaan-Nya),","arabic":"ٱلَّذِي خَلَقَ فَسَوَّىٰ","category":["87 (Al-A'la)","Al-A'la","Surah Al-A'la"],"ayahNumber":5950,"juzNumber":30,"footnotes":"","lang":"id"},{"name":"87:3","price":"yang menentukan kadar (masing-masing) dan memberi petunjuk,","arabic":"وَٱلَّذِي قَدَّرَ فَهَدَىٰ","category":["87 (Al-A'la)","Al-A'la","Surah Al-A'la"],"ayahNumber":5951,"juzNumber":30,"footnotes":"","lang":"id"},{"name":"87:4","price":"dan Yang menumbuhkan rerumputan,","arabic":"وَٱلَّذِيٓ أَخۡرَجَ ٱلۡمَرۡعَىٰ","category":["87 (Al-A'la)","Al-A'la","Surah Al-A'la"],"ayahNumber":5952,"juzNumber":30,"footnotes":"","lang":"id"},{"name":"87:5","price":"lalu dijadikan-Nya (rumput-rumput) itu kering kehitam-hitaman.","arabic":"فَجَعَلَهُۥ غُثَآءً أَحۡوَىٰ","category":["87 (Al-A'la)","Al-A'la","Surah Al-A'la"],"ayahNumber":5953,"juzNumber":30,"footnotes":"","lang":"id"},{"name":"87:6","price":"Kami akan membacakan (Al-Qur`an) kepadamu (Muhammad) sehingga engkau tidak akan lupa,","arabic":"سَنُقۡرِئُكَ فَلَا تَنسَىٰٓ","category":["87 (Al-A'la)","Al-A'la","Surah Al-A'la"],"ayahNumber":5954,"juzNumber":30,"footnotes":"","lang":"id"},{"name":"87:7","price":"kecuali jika Allah menghendaki. Sungguh, Dia mengetahui yang terang dan yang tersembunyi.","arabic":"إِلَّا مَا شَآءَ ٱللَّهُۚ إِنَّهُۥ يَعۡلَمُ ٱلۡجَهۡرَ وَمَا يَخۡفَىٰ","category":["87 (Al-A'la)","Al-A'la","Surah Al-A'la"],"ayahNumber":5955,"juzNumber":30,"footnotes":"","lang":"id"},{"name":"87:8","price":"Dan Kami akan memudahkan bagimu ke jalan kemudahan (mencapai kebahagian dunia dan akhirat),","arabic":"وَنُيَسِّرُكَ لِلۡيُسۡرَىٰ","category":["87 (Al-A'la)","Al-A'la","Surah Al-A'la"],"ayahNumber":5956,"juzNumber":30,"footnotes":"","lang":"id"},{"name":"87:9","price":"oleh sebab itu berikanlah peringatan, karena peringatan itu bermanfaat,","arabic":"فَذَكِّرۡ إِن نَّفَعَتِ ٱلذِّكۡرَىٰ","category":["87 (Al-A'la)","Al-A'la","Surah Al-A'la"],"ayahNumber":5957,"juzNumber":30,"footnotes":"","lang":"id"},{"name":"87:10","price":"orang yang takut (kepada Allah) akan mendapat pelajaran,","arabic":"سَيَذَّكَّرُ مَن يَخۡشَىٰ","category":["87 (Al-A'la)","Al-A'la","Surah Al-A'la"],"ayahNumber":5958,"juzNumber":30,"footnotes":"","lang":"id"},{"name":"87:11","price":"dan orang yang celaka (kafir) akan menjauhinya,","arabic":"وَيَتَجَنَّبُهَا ٱلۡأَشۡقَى","category":["87 (Al-A'la)","Al-A'la","Surah Al-A'la"],"ayahNumber":5959,"juzNumber":30,"footnotes":"","lang":"id"},{"name":"87:12","price":"(yaitu) orang yang akan memasuki api yang besar (neraka),","arabic":"ٱلَّذِي يَصۡلَى ٱلنَّارَ ٱلۡكُبۡرَىٰ","category":["87 (Al-A'la)","Al-A'la","Surah Al-A'la"],"ayahNumber":5960,"juzNumber":30,"footnotes":"","lang":"id"},{"name":"87:13","price":"selanjutnya dia di sana tidak mati dan tidak (pula) hidup.","arabic":"ثُمَّ لَا يَمُوتُ فِيهَا وَلَا يَحۡيَىٰ","category":["87 (Al-A'la)","Al-A'la","Surah Al-A'la"],"ayahNumber":5961,"juzNumber":30,"footnotes":"","lang":"id"},{"name":"87:14","price":"Sungguh beruntung orang yang menyucikan diri (dengan beriman),","arabic":"قَدۡ أَفۡلَحَ مَن تَزَكَّىٰ","category":["87 (Al-A'la)","Al-A'la","Surah Al-A'la"],"ayahNumber":5962,"juzNumber":30,"footnotes":"","lang":"id"},{"name":"87:15","price":"dan mengingat nama Tuhannya, lalu dia salat.","arabic":"وَذَكَرَ ٱسۡمَ رَبِّهِۦ فَصَلَّىٰ","category":["87 (Al-A'la)","Al-A'la","Surah Al-A'la"],"ayahNumber":5963,"juzNumber":30,"footnotes":"","lang":"id"},{"name":"87:16","price":"Sedangkan kamu (orang-orang kafir) memilih kehidupan dunia,","arabic":"بَلۡ تُؤۡثِرُونَ ٱلۡحَيَوٰةَ ٱلدُّنۡيَا","category":["87 (Al-A'la)","Al-A'la","Surah Al-A'la"],"ayahNumber":5964,"juzNumber":30,"footnotes":"","lang":"id"},{"name":"87:17","price":"padahal kehidupan a